1
00:00:11,105 --> 00:00:13,039
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">You don't have a girlfriend now, right?</font>

2
00:00:13,105 --> 00:00:15,839
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I heard that your only love is ramen,
and you don't have a girlfriend.</font>

3
00:00:16,338 --> 00:00:17,371
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Jeez, what should I do?</font>

4
00:00:22,972 --> 00:00:24,638
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Hey! What're you doing?</font>

5
00:00:24,705 --> 00:00:26,072
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">This here is my girlfriend!</font>

6
00:00:26,138 --> 00:00:28,072
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">So, I'm sorry, I can't go out with you.</font>

7
00:00:34,305 --> 00:00:35,872
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Yow! That's hot!</font>

8
00:00:35,939 --> 00:00:38,105
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I put my hand right in the pot!</font>

9
00:00:40,672 --> 00:00:42,371
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">CLOSED FOR PREPARATION</font>

10
00:00:42,538 --> 00:00:44,772
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">It started about a month ago.</font>

11
00:00:46,271 --> 00:00:51,371
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Just before closing she... Yukari...</font>

12
00:00:52,672 --> 00:00:55,872
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I don't know why, but she was crying
while she ate her ramen.</font>

13
00:00:58,305 --> 00:01:00,538
<font face="sans-serif" size="71"><i>I wanted to cheer her up somehow.</i></font>

14
00:01:01,238 --> 00:01:04,371
<font face="sans-serif" size="71"><i>So I gave her a free soft-boiled egg.</i></font>

15
00:01:04,438 --> 00:01:06,438
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Here. It's on the house.</font>

16
00:01:14,039 --> 00:01:15,039
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">That's all?</font>

17
00:01:18,939 --> 00:01:20,705
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">The next day</font>

18
00:01:21,039 --> 00:01:23,805
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">she said, "Please be my boyfriend."</font>

19
00:01:24,972 --> 00:01:28,905
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I turned her down, but she won't give up.</font>

20
00:01:28,972 --> 00:01:32,105
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">But even so, why did you lie like that?</font>

21
00:01:32,572 --> 00:01:34,072
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">That's not like you at all, Issei.</font>

22
00:01:35,305 --> 00:01:38,772
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">But lately Yukari's been
phoning our house,</font>

23
00:01:38,972 --> 00:01:41,105
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">and waiting for me outside.</font>

24
00:01:42,905 --> 00:01:45,605
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">She was waiting out front
when we came to prep.</font>

25
00:01:45,905 --> 00:01:50,472
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">At prep time? That's 5 a.m.!</font>

26
00:01:51,905 --> 00:01:54,872
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">If things get any worse,</font>

27
00:01:54,939 --> 00:01:56,572
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I won't be able to concentrate on work.</font>

28
00:01:56,638 --> 00:01:59,939
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Then why don't you flat out reject her?</font>

29
00:02:03,939 --> 00:02:06,072
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Yeah, that's right, Issei.</font>

30
00:02:07,638 --> 00:02:10,005
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">It doesn't matter
if she ends up hating you.</font>

31
00:02:10,072 --> 00:02:12,538
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">You've got to keep telling her
until she understands.</font>

32
00:02:14,839 --> 00:02:16,271
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Yukari...</font>

33
00:02:19,438 --> 00:02:21,772
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">she tells me
that our ramen is really delicious.</font>

34
00:02:22,738 --> 00:02:27,138
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I can't be so cold to a customer
that says good things about our ramen.</font>

35
00:02:29,005 --> 00:02:30,171
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Issei!</font>

36
00:02:30,238 --> 00:02:33,605
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">You are truly my son!
You're the real Evening Star!</font>

37
00:02:33,672 --> 00:02:35,039
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Father!</font>

38
00:02:37,472 --> 00:02:39,238
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Uhm...</font>

39
00:02:39,305 --> 00:02:40,872
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">-Oh, wait.
-Huh?</font>

40
00:02:43,371 --> 00:02:45,538
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">-I beg you!
-What?</font>

41
00:02:46,939 --> 00:02:48,738
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">While you're here at the shop...</font>

42
00:02:49,538 --> 00:02:52,939
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">No, just while Yukari is here,</font>

43
00:02:53,872 --> 00:02:55,905
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">please act like you're my girlfriend.</font>

44
00:02:56,839 --> 00:02:58,005
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Please!</font>

45
00:03:00,271 --> 00:03:02,072
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Don't do that.</font>

46
00:03:02,171 --> 00:03:04,605
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">When you bow down to me like that,</font>

47
00:03:04,672 --> 00:03:06,738
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">it feels so wrong.</font>

48
00:03:09,138 --> 00:03:10,305
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Oh, yeah.</font>

49
00:03:12,672 --> 00:03:14,005
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">You're right.</font>

50
00:03:14,538 --> 00:03:15,605
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Huh?</font>

51
00:03:17,138 --> 00:03:19,905
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">The money you owe
for the broken dishes is $12,000.</font>

52
00:03:19,972 --> 00:03:22,738
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Who's letting you secretly pay that off
in installments?</font>

53
00:03:25,772 --> 00:03:27,039
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Wait a minute!</font>

54
00:03:27,138 --> 00:03:29,605
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">That has nothing to do with this!</font>

55
00:03:29,672 --> 00:03:31,705
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">What are you whispering about?</font>

56
00:03:31,939 --> 00:03:34,039
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Oh, nothing.</font>

57
00:03:36,672 --> 00:03:40,438
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">At any rate,
I've already got a proper boyfriend.</font>

58
00:03:43,105 --> 00:03:44,438
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I can't deal with you guys.</font>

59
00:03:45,939 --> 00:03:48,472
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Hey! Wait for me, Uehara!</font>

60
00:03:48,672 --> 00:03:54,772
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">EVENING STAR</font>

61
00:03:57,072 --> 00:03:59,972
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">You're OK with that, Uehara?</font>

62
00:04:00,039 --> 00:04:03,371
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I can act the part
of another guy's girlfriend?</font>

63
00:04:03,438 --> 00:04:04,805
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I don't care.</font>

64
00:04:04,872 --> 00:04:08,572
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">-You're just faking it, right?
-Well, yeah, but--</font>

65
00:04:08,638 --> 00:04:11,438
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Anyway, it's really cold. Let's go home!</font>

66
00:04:13,772 --> 00:04:15,171
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">What's with him?</font>

67
00:04:19,138 --> 00:04:19,972
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Darn him!</font>

68
00:04:31,638 --> 00:04:33,305
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">We can't go in now.</font>

69
00:04:36,972 --> 00:04:39,505
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I told you, we can't go in now!</font>

70
00:04:42,271 --> 00:04:44,738
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">-Let's go, Tetsu.
-Yeah, let's.</font>

71
00:04:50,005 --> 00:04:54,438
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">That's the first time
I've seen a real live kiss.</font>

72
00:04:55,305 --> 00:04:57,472
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">And right in front of us, too!</font>

73
00:04:59,472 --> 00:05:01,572
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Jeez! Who want's to see that?</font>

74
00:05:13,572 --> 00:05:15,705
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I guess that's normal.</font>

75
00:05:15,772 --> 00:05:17,805
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">An elevator is pretty isolated.</font>

76
00:05:17,872 --> 00:05:21,338
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">You see it all the time in movies.</font>

77
00:05:22,939 --> 00:05:26,271
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">But it's not like I want to kiss here too</font>

78
00:05:26,338 --> 00:05:28,705
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">just because it's isolated.</font>

79
00:05:30,371 --> 00:05:32,738
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">What the heck are you mumbling about?</font>

80
00:05:37,438 --> 00:05:39,405
<font face="sans-serif" size="71"><i>You're supposed to be Issei's girlfriend?</i></font>

81
00:05:39,472 --> 00:05:41,872
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Yeah. And what's worse,</font>

82
00:05:41,939 --> 00:05:45,105
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Issei tried to blackmail me with
the money I owe for the broken dishes.</font>

83
00:05:45,472 --> 00:05:48,839
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">But it's just while
that woman's at the shop, right?</font>

84
00:05:48,905 --> 00:05:50,638
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">-Yeah.
-What's wrong with that?</font>

85
00:05:53,205 --> 00:05:54,505
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Oh, sorry.</font>

86
00:05:56,505 --> 00:05:59,072
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Sheesh! What a pain!</font>

87
00:06:01,772 --> 00:06:03,371
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Huh? What is it?</font>

88
00:06:05,238 --> 00:06:08,605
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Just because I didn't text him
for a while yesterday, he's all jealous.</font>

89
00:06:08,672 --> 00:06:10,772
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">From: Mitsuishi
I tried contacting you all day yesterday!</font>

90
00:06:10,839 --> 00:06:12,939
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Mitsuishi's worried about you.</font>

91
00:06:14,205 --> 00:06:17,738
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">It wasn't like a group date!
We were just doing karaoke.</font>

92
00:06:17,805 --> 00:06:22,538
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Yeah, some guys were there,
but he's getting way too possessive.</font>

93
00:06:23,371 --> 00:06:26,538
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">-I wish Uehara were more possessive.
-Huh?</font>

94
00:06:27,772 --> 00:06:32,638
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">That's so much more boyfriend-like.</font>

95
00:06:32,905 --> 00:06:35,371
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">What are you talking about?</font>

96
00:06:35,438 --> 00:06:38,905
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">You're the one with the boyfriend
that everyone wants.</font>

97
00:06:40,772 --> 00:06:42,839
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Is he really my boyfriend?</font>

98
00:06:44,205 --> 00:06:46,171
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I can't deal with you guys.</font>

99
00:06:46,405 --> 00:06:49,005
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Anyway, it's really cold. Let's go home!</font>

100
00:07:14,939 --> 00:07:16,472
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">-One Miso Ramen!
-OK!</font>

101
00:07:16,538 --> 00:07:18,271
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I'll take care of this, Nao.
You get them.</font>

102
00:07:18,338 --> 00:07:19,839
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">OK.</font>

103
00:07:20,138 --> 00:07:21,472
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Here's your water.</font>

104
00:07:21,538 --> 00:07:24,205
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I told you,
I came right home after the karaoke.</font>

105
00:07:24,271 --> 00:07:27,271
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">But you still could have texted me,
right?</font>

106
00:07:27,338 --> 00:07:28,405
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Jeez! Quit being so nosy!</font>

107
00:07:28,472 --> 00:07:30,605
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I'm not being nosy!</font>

108
00:07:30,672 --> 00:07:33,839
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">OK, you two! Enough! This is on me.</font>

109
00:07:33,905 --> 00:07:35,438
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">-Really?
-Thanks!</font>

110
00:07:35,505 --> 00:07:37,605
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Would you two make up already?</font>

111
00:07:46,105 --> 00:07:47,638
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">-How is it?
-Yum! Good!</font>

112
00:07:50,638 --> 00:07:53,072
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Nao, that woman's been glaring
at you for a while.</font>

113
00:07:53,138 --> 00:07:54,238
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Huh?</font>

114
00:07:59,839 --> 00:08:01,605
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">She's been here since this morning.</font>

115
00:08:01,672 --> 00:08:03,105
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Since this morning?</font>

116
00:08:03,271 --> 00:08:05,538
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Is that Issei's stalker?</font>

117
00:08:05,672 --> 00:08:06,572
<font face="sans-serif" size="71"><i>Thanks! That was great!</i></font>

118
00:08:06,638 --> 00:08:07,672
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Yeah.</font>

119
00:08:07,738 --> 00:08:09,705
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Oh, you're supposed to
act like the girlfriend--</font>

120
00:08:09,772 --> 00:08:13,271
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Shh! She'll hear you! She'll hear!</font>

121
00:08:15,105 --> 00:08:17,472
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Dang, what a negative attitude she's got!</font>

122
00:08:18,105 --> 00:08:20,338
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Hey, Nao. Clean up the counter.</font>

123
00:08:20,572 --> 00:08:22,472
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Uh... OK.</font>

124
00:08:43,672 --> 00:08:44,705
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Oh! Oh!</font>

125
00:08:44,972 --> 00:08:48,872
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">How about... How about some water?</font>

126
00:08:48,939 --> 00:08:50,872
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Here's some water.</font>

127
00:08:50,939 --> 00:08:53,072
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">-You're a liar.
-Huh?</font>

128
00:08:54,138 --> 00:08:57,072
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">You and Issei aren't a couple.
That's a lie, isn't it?</font>

129
00:08:58,572 --> 00:09:00,638
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Oh... No...</font>

130
00:09:01,472 --> 00:09:02,972
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">No, that's not...</font>

131
00:09:03,638 --> 00:09:05,305
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">-Issei!
-Yes?</font>

132
00:09:05,872 --> 00:09:08,772
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Will you go on a date with me tomorrow?</font>

133
00:09:08,839 --> 00:09:09,738
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">What?</font>

134
00:09:09,805 --> 00:09:12,705
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I'm not giving up
until you go on a date with me.</font>

135
00:09:12,772 --> 00:09:14,138
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">What are you talking about?</font>

136
00:09:14,205 --> 00:09:16,638
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I've got a girlfriend.</font>

137
00:09:16,872 --> 00:09:18,305
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Isn't that right?</font>

138
00:09:25,072 --> 00:09:28,171
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Give it up.
You can't fool me any more.</font>

139
00:09:28,638 --> 00:09:31,705
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">We're not trying to fool you.</font>

140
00:09:31,772 --> 00:09:35,972
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">If you're going together,
then why aren't you friendlier to her?</font>

141
00:09:36,605 --> 00:09:39,738
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Well, uh... because we're working.</font>

142
00:09:39,939 --> 00:09:41,705
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Isn't that right, Nao?</font>

143
00:09:43,371 --> 00:09:45,005
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Yeah...</font>

144
00:09:45,072 --> 00:09:47,638
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">And you never ever touch each other.</font>

145
00:09:49,039 --> 00:09:50,371
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">That's not true!</font>

146
00:09:51,438 --> 00:09:53,939
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Uh... yeah...</font>

147
00:09:54,005 --> 00:09:57,472
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">You two don't give off
a lovey-dovey aura at all.</font>

148
00:09:58,772 --> 00:10:01,472
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Lovey-dovey aura?</font>

149
00:10:01,538 --> 00:10:03,138
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">-I love you, Nao!
-Huh?</font>

150
00:10:05,371 --> 00:10:07,905
<font face="sans-serif" size="71"><i>When did you two get together?</i></font>

151
00:10:09,905 --> 00:10:13,972
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Nao... you and Issei are...</font>

152
00:10:14,039 --> 00:10:15,605
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">No, no, we're not, Abe!</font>

153
00:10:15,672 --> 00:10:17,205
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Yes, we are!</font>

154
00:10:17,271 --> 00:10:18,238
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Issei!</font>

155
00:10:18,305 --> 00:10:21,271
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">She's got a boy--</font>

156
00:10:21,338 --> 00:10:23,405
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Boy, you sure want to eat curry,
don't you?</font>

157
00:10:23,472 --> 00:10:25,138
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">But this is a ramen shop.</font>

158
00:10:25,205 --> 00:10:26,605
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Here! Have some potstickers!</font>

159
00:10:26,672 --> 00:10:28,572
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">-Marina, get some soy sauce.
-Here you go!</font>

160
00:10:28,638 --> 00:10:32,905
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">No, there's something fishy going on.
You're hiding something.</font>

161
00:10:35,772 --> 00:10:38,238
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">No... No, not at all.</font>

162
00:10:38,972 --> 00:10:41,572
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">At any rate, we really are a couple.</font>

163
00:10:41,805 --> 00:10:43,638
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Then prove it to me.</font>

164
00:10:44,138 --> 00:10:45,572
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Show me proof that you're lovey-dovey.</font>

165
00:10:45,738 --> 00:10:47,738
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Proof?</font>

166
00:10:47,939 --> 00:10:51,405
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Show me all day tomorrow.</font>

167
00:10:51,472 --> 00:10:54,939
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Huh? What do you mean by that?</font>

168
00:10:57,371 --> 00:10:59,538
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Huh?
The three of you are going on a date?</font>

169
00:10:59,872 --> 00:11:01,405
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Uh-huh.</font>

170
00:11:02,205 --> 00:11:05,705
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">It just kind of ended up
that the three of us would go together.</font>

171
00:11:05,772 --> 00:11:07,205
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Really?</font>

172
00:11:08,005 --> 00:11:10,538
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Issei was at a loss for what to do.</font>

173
00:11:10,705 --> 00:11:14,472
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">So he said if that would satisfy her,
then he'd do it.</font>

174
00:11:16,205 --> 00:11:19,072
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Oh, but don't worry, Uehara.</font>

175
00:11:19,171 --> 00:11:23,138
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">We're only doing this to convince Yukari.</font>

176
00:11:25,839 --> 00:11:31,839
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">But... if you really don't want me to go,
I can tell them no.</font>

177
00:11:31,905 --> 00:11:32,772
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Go! Go!</font>

178
00:11:34,271 --> 00:11:35,672
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Yes!</font>

179
00:11:37,271 --> 00:11:38,772
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Huh? Were you saying something?</font>

180
00:11:41,572 --> 00:11:43,072
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Forget about it.</font>

181
00:11:43,338 --> 00:11:44,939
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I'm taking a bath.</font>

182
00:11:53,005 --> 00:11:55,805
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Is he really my boyfriend?</font>

183
00:11:58,972 --> 00:12:00,772
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">FAKE DATE DAY</font>

184
00:12:01,472 --> 00:12:03,839
<font face="sans-serif" size="71"><i>Wow, what a nice day!</i></font>

185
00:12:04,005 --> 00:12:07,271
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">There's only a slight breeze.
It's perfect date weather.</font>

186
00:12:07,839 --> 00:12:08,839
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Don't you agree, Nao?</font>

187
00:12:08,905 --> 00:12:12,039
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I'm not sure I can do this.</font>

188
00:12:12,472 --> 00:12:15,039
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I'm really sorry to make you do this.</font>

189
00:12:15,105 --> 00:12:16,905
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">But this will be the end of it.</font>

190
00:12:16,972 --> 00:12:19,772
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Just play my girlfriend for today.</font>

191
00:12:19,839 --> 00:12:20,738
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I know.</font>

192
00:12:24,305 --> 00:12:25,572
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I'm here.</font>

193
00:12:29,039 --> 00:12:30,505
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Hello.</font>

194
00:12:32,205 --> 00:12:36,271
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Thank you for letting me watch you today.</font>

195
00:12:38,472 --> 00:12:40,538
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Sure, you're welcome.</font>

196
00:12:44,238 --> 00:12:46,972
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Dang, computers are expensive.</font>

197
00:12:49,438 --> 00:12:52,205
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">This is no time to be casually
flipping through a magazine.</font>

198
00:12:52,271 --> 00:12:54,572
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Cut that out, you jerk.</font>

199
00:12:55,205 --> 00:12:59,371
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I came here to advise you
as your close friend.</font>

200
00:12:59,438 --> 00:13:01,472
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">-Since when are you my close friend?
-Ouch!</font>

201
00:13:01,538 --> 00:13:03,438
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Listen to me, and don't be too surprised.</font>

202
00:13:03,872 --> 00:13:08,305
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Nao and the guy Issei she works for...</font>

203
00:13:09,072 --> 00:13:10,438
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">are dating!</font>

204
00:13:11,972 --> 00:13:14,039
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I'm serious! I saw them!</font>

205
00:13:14,105 --> 00:13:16,271
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">OK, fine. Now get out of here.</font>

206
00:13:16,338 --> 00:13:18,572
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I've got my own work to go to.</font>

207
00:13:18,738 --> 00:13:21,338
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">-Uehara!
-Crap! I'm going to be late.</font>

208
00:13:22,205 --> 00:13:25,805
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Jeez! You handsome guys
sure don't have to worry much.</font>

209
00:13:26,605 --> 00:13:29,238
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">When Issei put his arm
around Nao like that</font>

210
00:13:29,505 --> 00:13:32,438
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">it totally ticked me off,
and I'm not even her boyfriend.</font>

211
00:13:34,138 --> 00:13:36,039
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">What should we ride first?</font>

212
00:13:37,271 --> 00:13:39,072
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Probably something scary is best.</font>

213
00:13:39,705 --> 00:13:41,039
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Right...</font>

214
00:13:42,371 --> 00:13:43,538
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Nao?</font>

215
00:13:45,738 --> 00:13:47,505
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Yeah!</font>

216
00:13:59,738 --> 00:14:01,772
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Oh, that looks good.</font>

217
00:14:01,839 --> 00:14:04,171
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Let's ride that. Come on.</font>

218
00:14:07,238 --> 00:14:09,872
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I wish I could have come here with Uehara.</font>

219
00:14:14,438 --> 00:14:16,538
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">-No, not that one.
-Why not?</font>

220
00:14:17,405 --> 00:14:18,405
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">It'll be fun.</font>

221
00:14:18,672 --> 00:14:21,039
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Can you believe that the three of them
are on a date together?</font>

222
00:14:21,438 --> 00:14:24,438
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">But why do we have to watch them?</font>

223
00:14:24,505 --> 00:14:28,039
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">We're doing this for Nao's sake.</font>

224
00:14:28,405 --> 00:14:30,572
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">How is this for Nao?</font>

225
00:14:30,738 --> 00:14:34,238
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I'm calling this
Operation Set His Heart on Fire!</font>

226
00:14:35,039 --> 00:14:36,839
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">-Oh. There they are!
-I brought him.</font>

227
00:14:36,905 --> 00:14:38,905
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">What the heck are you guys
also doing here?</font>

228
00:14:38,972 --> 00:14:44,805
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">We're all making sure
that Nao doesn't do anything foolish.</font>

229
00:14:44,872 --> 00:14:47,005
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">This is dumb.
Don't you have anything better to do?</font>

230
00:14:47,072 --> 00:14:49,672
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Aah! Uehara! Have a look! Have a look!</font>

231
00:14:49,738 --> 00:14:51,939
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">-Huh?
-Look! Look! Look!</font>

232
00:14:52,005 --> 00:14:53,538
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Hide!</font>

233
00:15:01,238 --> 00:15:03,171
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">She's supposed to be acting,</font>

234
00:15:03,238 --> 00:15:06,238
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">but that's going too far.</font>

235
00:15:11,105 --> 00:15:13,672
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I'm so worried about her.</font>

236
00:15:13,738 --> 00:15:16,905
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">As her best friend, I'm concerned.</font>

237
00:15:17,138 --> 00:15:20,772
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">What if things escalate
between those two?</font>

238
00:15:21,805 --> 00:15:24,738
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Just let go of everything
and have a great time today, OK?</font>

239
00:15:25,039 --> 00:15:28,638
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">-I'm not sure I can.
-Don't you like this kind of ride?</font>

240
00:15:28,772 --> 00:15:30,705
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Yes, I do. It's just that...</font>

241
00:15:32,072 --> 00:15:33,472
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Something is giving me a chill.</font>

242
00:15:44,605 --> 00:15:47,171
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Oh, no. I'm scared, Uehara.</font>

243
00:15:47,238 --> 00:15:49,005
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Get your hands off me, jerk.</font>

244
00:15:49,072 --> 00:15:53,405
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I feel so guilty that it seems like
I can hear Uehara's voice.</font>

245
00:15:53,738 --> 00:15:55,405
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">You got his approval, right?</font>

246
00:15:56,538 --> 00:15:58,438
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">-Yeah, but...
-Uehara!</font>

247
00:15:58,905 --> 00:16:00,672
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I just don't feel right about it.</font>

248
00:16:00,738 --> 00:16:01,805
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">With all these couples here,</font>

249
00:16:01,872 --> 00:16:04,072
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">it makes me think about Uehara.
I wish he were here.</font>

250
00:16:13,939 --> 00:16:16,472
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">-That was a real surprise.
-It sure was.</font>

251
00:16:18,271 --> 00:16:20,805
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">-That was more fun than I expected.
-Yeah, it was.</font>

252
00:16:21,072 --> 00:16:24,672
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">-This is too much.
-It's only a merry-go-round, Issei!</font>

253
00:16:25,872 --> 00:16:27,072
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Have they always gone this fast?</font>

254
00:16:27,171 --> 00:16:29,738
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">-Look how much it's going up and down!
-It sure is.</font>

255
00:16:32,405 --> 00:16:34,472
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Oh! Mount Fuji!</font>

256
00:16:34,738 --> 00:16:37,171
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Hey, look, Yukari!
You can see Mount Fuji!</font>

257
00:16:38,171 --> 00:16:41,005
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">-Fuji's totally gigantic!
-It's huge!</font>

258
00:16:41,072 --> 00:16:42,438
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Look! Can you see it?</font>

259
00:16:42,505 --> 00:16:44,872
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">-It sure is pretty.
-Wow!</font>

260
00:16:44,939 --> 00:16:46,039
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">-It's nice.
-Yeah.</font>

261
00:16:51,171 --> 00:16:55,371
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Hey, this is so much fun!
How come you're not riding it?</font>

262
00:16:55,438 --> 00:16:56,438
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">See!</font>

263
00:16:59,805 --> 00:17:02,438
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">She's totally gotten into it now.</font>

264
00:17:34,638 --> 00:17:36,072
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Look, Uehara!
What cool french fries!</font>

265
00:17:36,171 --> 00:17:37,138
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Shut up!</font>

266
00:17:38,705 --> 00:17:41,972
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Very nice. It seems
his heart's starting to catch fire.</font>

267
00:17:42,472 --> 00:17:44,405
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">That's kind of cruel, you know.</font>

268
00:17:44,472 --> 00:17:47,338
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Who cares. I'm doing this for Nao.</font>

269
00:17:51,905 --> 00:17:53,138
<font face="sans-serif" size="71"><i>You're terrible at this.</i></font>

270
00:17:53,672 --> 00:17:55,072
<font face="sans-serif" size="71"><i>You're pretty bad too.</i></font>

271
00:17:55,138 --> 00:17:57,405
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Wait, Issei! Wait!</font>

272
00:18:02,305 --> 00:18:05,205
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I haven't been to an amusement park
in a while. It sure is fun!</font>

273
00:18:05,271 --> 00:18:06,238
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">-Isn't it?
-Yeah.</font>

274
00:18:06,305 --> 00:18:08,572
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">-Doing this is nice once in a while.
-It is!</font>

275
00:18:10,072 --> 00:18:12,438
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">-Oh!
-What?</font>

276
00:18:12,505 --> 00:18:15,205
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Next let's do something
that you want to do, Yukari.</font>

277
00:18:15,472 --> 00:18:17,738
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I don't really care. Anything is fine.</font>

278
00:18:18,538 --> 00:18:22,472
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Oh, come on. Since you're here,
you may as well have fun.</font>

279
00:18:25,638 --> 00:18:29,872
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Or, maybe,
you've become convinced about us?</font>

280
00:18:30,839 --> 00:18:32,371
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Oh, yeah. That's right.</font>

281
00:18:32,438 --> 00:18:35,572
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I was just plain having a good time.</font>

282
00:18:35,872 --> 00:18:37,039
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Yukari,</font>

283
00:18:37,371 --> 00:18:40,772
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I would hope that you could still be
a regular customer</font>

284
00:18:40,839 --> 00:18:43,205
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">-like you have been, and--
-I'm not convinced!</font>

285
00:18:43,638 --> 00:18:48,305
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I still don't believe
that you're a couple.</font>

286
00:18:48,371 --> 00:18:49,205
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Yukari--</font>

287
00:18:49,271 --> 00:18:51,405
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">You want me to choose the next ride,
right?</font>

288
00:18:52,305 --> 00:18:53,138
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Uh-huh.</font>

289
00:18:53,505 --> 00:18:56,705
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I've decided what I want to do.</font>

290
00:18:57,405 --> 00:18:58,238
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Which one?</font>

291
00:19:01,472 --> 00:19:04,039
<font face="sans-serif" size="71"><i>No! No! No! No!</i></font>

292
00:19:22,939 --> 00:19:25,839
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Open the door! Come on! Open the door!</font>

293
00:19:29,905 --> 00:19:32,772
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">JIKYU GENERAL HOSPITAL</font>

294
00:19:44,072 --> 00:19:45,738
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I can't take this!</font>

295
00:19:47,371 --> 00:19:49,672
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">No! No! Go away!</font>

296
00:19:55,538 --> 00:19:57,772
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Uhm, is the exit this way?</font>

297
00:20:00,438 --> 00:20:02,505
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Uh, this sure must be hard work.</font>

298
00:20:02,572 --> 00:20:04,438
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">By the way, my name is Abe Jun.</font>

299
00:20:04,505 --> 00:20:06,005
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Everybody calls me Abe--</font>

300
00:20:06,072 --> 00:20:08,605
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Jeez, Abe! Let's get going!
Sorry about that.</font>

301
00:20:08,672 --> 00:20:11,138
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">How can you hit on girls
in a place like this?</font>

302
00:20:11,672 --> 00:20:13,738
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Jeez! That scared me!</font>

303
00:20:14,405 --> 00:20:15,238
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">How's this job?</font>

304
00:20:20,772 --> 00:20:22,472
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I can't take any more of this.</font>

305
00:20:23,138 --> 00:20:25,972
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I can even hear Marina's voice.</font>

306
00:20:26,039 --> 00:20:27,972
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I must be hearing phantoms.</font>

307
00:20:29,072 --> 00:20:31,738
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I'm so afraid, I'm losing my mind.</font>

308
00:20:34,905 --> 00:20:37,405
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I want to go home!</font>

309
00:20:42,605 --> 00:20:44,538
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">-What are you doing there?
-No! Leave me alone!</font>

310
00:20:44,605 --> 00:20:47,371
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Quit screaming! It's me!</font>

311
00:20:47,872 --> 00:20:49,438
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">-Look! Look!
-I'm scared.</font>

312
00:20:49,505 --> 00:20:51,171
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">It's me! Look!</font>

313
00:20:53,872 --> 00:20:57,238
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Uehara... Why are you here?</font>

314
00:20:57,305 --> 00:20:59,772
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I could ask you the same.
Why are you alone?</font>

315
00:21:06,005 --> 00:21:08,105
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I so wanted to be with you.</font>

316
00:21:19,405 --> 00:21:20,672
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Let's go.</font>

317
00:21:22,905 --> 00:21:24,072
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Come with me.</font>

318
00:21:25,705 --> 00:21:26,872
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">OK.</font>

319
00:21:41,672 --> 00:21:45,205
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">JIKYU GENERAL HOSPITAL</font>

320
00:21:46,505 --> 00:21:47,738
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Nao!</font>

321
00:21:52,271 --> 00:21:54,338
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Huh?</font>

322
00:21:54,705 --> 00:21:57,271
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">What are all you guys doing here?</font>

323
00:21:57,438 --> 00:22:02,638
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Well, to tell you the truth,
I happened to receive some tickets.</font>

324
00:22:02,705 --> 00:22:05,705
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">But we didn't want to interfere.
Right, Mitsuishi?</font>

325
00:22:05,772 --> 00:22:08,772
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Yeah. We didn't say anything,
and did different stuff.</font>

326
00:22:10,472 --> 00:22:12,005
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Who's this good-looking guy?</font>

327
00:22:14,472 --> 00:22:18,572
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Oh, uh... Uehara, he's...</font>

328
00:22:18,638 --> 00:22:20,472
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">He's a classmate. A classmate!</font>

329
00:22:20,538 --> 00:22:22,305
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">-We're all Nao's classmates.
-That's right.</font>

330
00:22:26,939 --> 00:22:28,438
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I see.</font>

331
00:22:30,138 --> 00:22:32,072
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">By the way,</font>

332
00:22:32,171 --> 00:22:34,205
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">-there's another great ride.
-What's that?</font>

333
00:22:34,805 --> 00:22:38,305
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">The Ferris wheel here
has these four gondolas</font>

334
00:22:38,371 --> 00:22:40,138
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">that are completely see-through.</font>

335
00:22:40,205 --> 00:22:41,905
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Wow! Cool!</font>

336
00:22:41,972 --> 00:22:43,605
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">And there's this rumor</font>

337
00:22:43,672 --> 00:22:46,939
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">that if a couple rides in one of those
and kisses at the very top,</font>

338
00:22:47,005 --> 00:22:48,872
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">-they'll be happy forever!
-Yeah!</font>

339
00:22:48,939 --> 00:22:50,371
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Really?</font>

340
00:22:50,438 --> 00:22:54,005
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">That's so stupid. I'm going home.</font>

341
00:23:01,338 --> 00:23:02,371
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Come closer.</font>

342
00:23:03,572 --> 00:23:04,572
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Uehara.</font>

343
00:23:09,171 --> 00:23:10,171
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Nao.</font>

344
00:23:15,171 --> 00:23:16,305
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I want to ride that.</font>

345
00:23:17,305 --> 00:23:18,138
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">What?</font>

346
00:23:25,538 --> 00:23:27,171
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I really want to ride that!</font>

347
00:23:29,939 --> 00:23:31,939
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">TRANSPARENT GONDOLAS</font>

348
00:23:37,338 --> 00:23:42,171
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Even though I said that,
it's still going to be three of us.</font>

349
00:23:46,538 --> 00:23:49,505
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I'll hold back Yukari and Issei.</font>

350
00:23:49,572 --> 00:23:52,072
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">-Then you jump on with Uehara.
-What?</font>

351
00:23:52,171 --> 00:23:55,405
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I'll let you and him have
the see-through one.</font>

352
00:23:55,472 --> 00:23:57,271
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Get a kiss at the top! You can do it!</font>

353
00:24:02,638 --> 00:24:04,638
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">LOVER'S HOT SPOT
FERRIS WHEEL</font>

354
00:24:06,438 --> 00:24:07,472
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Marina.</font>

355
00:24:07,872 --> 00:24:10,805
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">It'll work out. Uehara wants it too.</font>

356
00:24:11,271 --> 00:24:12,939
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I know you're on the same wavelength.</font>

357
00:24:19,405 --> 00:24:20,572
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">OK.</font>

358
00:24:21,205 --> 00:24:23,238
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Ready? Let's do this.</font>

359
00:24:24,405 --> 00:24:25,605
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Ready... Go!</font>

360
00:24:29,705 --> 00:24:31,405
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Issei!</font>

361
00:24:33,905 --> 00:24:35,505
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Nao!</font>

362
00:24:37,238 --> 00:24:38,705
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Marina.</font>

363
00:24:41,338 --> 00:24:42,772
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Uehara!</font>

364
00:24:44,972 --> 00:24:47,238
<font face="sans-serif" size="71"><i>-Let's get on, Issei.
-You must be kidding!</i></font>

365
00:24:47,305 --> 00:24:49,772
<font face="sans-serif" size="71"><i>OK, Uehara and me ride together.</i></font>

366
00:24:49,839 --> 00:24:51,171
<font face="sans-serif" size="71"><i>Get your hands off me, you creep.</i></font>

367
00:24:51,772 --> 00:24:52,805
<font face="sans-serif" size="71"><i>Ouch!</i></font>

368
00:24:52,872 --> 00:24:55,039
<font face="sans-serif" size="71"><i>-I mean...
-Stop it!</i></font>

369
00:24:55,105 --> 00:24:56,505
<font face="sans-serif" size="71"><i>Stop it! Stop it!</i></font>

370
00:25:02,972 --> 00:25:05,538
<font face="sans-serif" size="71"><i>Come on! You're holding up the line!</i></font>

371
00:25:11,972 --> 00:25:16,205
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">What the... Why am I all alone in here?</font>

372
00:25:19,705 --> 00:25:20,538
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Where's Nao?</font>

373
00:25:22,505 --> 00:25:24,939
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Things got all messed up.</font>

374
00:25:27,072 --> 00:25:30,972
<font face="sans-serif" size="71"><i>What the... How did it end up like that?</i></font>

375
00:25:31,872 --> 00:25:33,972
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Just forget about it, would you?</font>

376
00:25:35,238 --> 00:25:37,338
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">How can you talk like that?</font>

377
00:25:40,438 --> 00:25:42,271
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I mean,
you don't have to go to all this trouble.</font>

378
00:25:42,338 --> 00:25:44,839
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Things will work out between Nao
and Uehara if you leave them alone.</font>

379
00:25:46,839 --> 00:25:50,905
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I'm not doing this... just for Nao.</font>

380
00:25:51,605 --> 00:25:52,438
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Huh?</font>

381
00:25:54,005 --> 00:25:56,605
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">We need a chance to make up too.</font>

382
00:26:09,705 --> 00:26:11,505
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Mitsuishi...</font>

383
00:26:12,705 --> 00:26:14,905
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">you can see what's going on with others,</font>

384
00:26:14,972 --> 00:26:18,305
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">but you can't tell when things are wrong
with yourself.</font>

385
00:26:28,039 --> 00:26:30,638
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Wow! Oh my god!</font>

386
00:26:31,005 --> 00:26:33,638
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Marina and Mitsuishi are...</font>

387
00:26:33,705 --> 00:26:36,772
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">kissing in the gondola!</font>

388
00:26:41,039 --> 00:26:44,772
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">They got there first.</font>

389
00:26:56,305 --> 00:26:58,905
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">We ended up as an odd pair, didn't we?</font>

390
00:27:00,505 --> 00:27:02,138
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Sorry.</font>

391
00:27:02,371 --> 00:27:04,405
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">No, it's all right.</font>

392
00:27:04,738 --> 00:27:07,205
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">It's actually been
a really fun day today.</font>

393
00:27:13,072 --> 00:27:14,738
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Uhm, Yukari.</font>

394
00:27:16,238 --> 00:27:18,572
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Why do you like Issei so much?</font>

395
00:27:21,705 --> 00:27:24,039
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Well, I mean...</font>

396
00:27:24,572 --> 00:27:27,271
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I don't really know you,</font>

397
00:27:28,039 --> 00:27:32,072
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">but you don't look like
the super aggressive type.</font>

398
00:27:34,805 --> 00:27:37,905
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Because he smiled at me.</font>

399
00:27:38,672 --> 00:27:39,672
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Huh?</font>

400
00:27:40,338 --> 00:27:44,271
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I've never been able to smile much.</font>

401
00:27:46,371 --> 00:27:49,605
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I was always alone, even in university.</font>

402
00:27:50,371 --> 00:27:53,705
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">One day, I got my courage up
and went to a group blind date.</font>

403
00:27:55,472 --> 00:27:58,039
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">But I couldn't join the conversation.</font>

404
00:27:59,138 --> 00:28:04,605
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Everybody would stare at me,
but act like they weren't.</font>

405
00:28:06,271 --> 00:28:07,738
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Then on my way home...</font>

406
00:28:14,238 --> 00:28:16,005
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Here. It's on the house.</font>

407
00:28:18,772 --> 00:28:20,939
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Your reward for working hard today.</font>

408
00:28:23,338 --> 00:28:25,271
<font face="sans-serif" size="71"><i>At that time</i></font>

409
00:28:25,338 --> 00:28:27,371
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">it felt like...</font>

410
00:28:27,972 --> 00:28:30,972
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Issei was the only person
who appreciated me for who I am.</font>

411
00:28:32,939 --> 00:28:38,005
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">So I began to wish
that I could spend more time with him.</font>

412
00:28:42,138 --> 00:28:44,672
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I know it was really
out of place for me to do that.</font>

413
00:28:44,738 --> 00:28:45,939
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">No, that's not true!</font>

414
00:28:50,972 --> 00:28:52,805
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">This is what Issei told me.</font>

415
00:28:54,438 --> 00:28:57,505
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">"Yukari said good things
about our ramen."</font>

416
00:28:59,271 --> 00:29:02,171
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">You've encouraged Issei, Yukari.</font>

417
00:29:02,805 --> 00:29:07,505
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I know that his smile was
just a smile for a customer.</font>

418
00:29:07,572 --> 00:29:10,039
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">-That's not true.
-I'm convinced.</font>

419
00:29:10,672 --> 00:29:15,138
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I've been convinced about you two
for a while.</font>

420
00:29:15,472 --> 00:29:16,638
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Huh?</font>

421
00:29:17,772 --> 00:29:21,205
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I was just being spiteful.</font>

422
00:29:23,438 --> 00:29:27,572
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">After being with you all day today,
I understand now.</font>

423
00:29:29,438 --> 00:29:31,939
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">If you can make Issei smile like that...</font>

424
00:29:33,738 --> 00:29:35,672
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">then I have to give up.</font>

425
00:29:36,939 --> 00:29:38,672
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Yukari...</font>

426
00:29:49,039 --> 00:29:50,005
<font face="sans-serif" size="71"><i>Sorry about</i></font>

427
00:29:50,872 --> 00:29:52,338
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">borrowing Nao today.</font>

428
00:29:53,538 --> 00:29:55,738
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">It's OK. She owes a lot to you.</font>

429
00:29:56,405 --> 00:29:58,238
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">But I bet it ticks you off, doesn't it?</font>

430
00:29:59,872 --> 00:30:00,972
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Not really.</font>

431
00:30:02,972 --> 00:30:03,939
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">You're OK with it?</font>

432
00:30:05,805 --> 00:30:07,271
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Yeah, I am.</font>

433
00:30:08,271 --> 00:30:09,271
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">How can you be?</font>

434
00:30:11,338 --> 00:30:13,538
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">It's not really my place to say this,</font>

435
00:30:13,738 --> 00:30:16,039
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">but when you act all cool like this,</font>

436
00:30:16,105 --> 00:30:17,738
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">it makes her feel anxious about you.</font>

437
00:30:25,538 --> 00:30:29,638
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">She's always smiling.</font>

438
00:30:30,271 --> 00:30:31,271
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Huh?</font>

439
00:30:31,338 --> 00:30:33,039
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">She also gets angry easily,</font>

440
00:30:34,438 --> 00:30:35,438
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">and cries easily too.</font>

441
00:30:39,138 --> 00:30:42,605
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">But she always ends up
with a smile on her face.</font>

442
00:30:46,672 --> 00:30:48,572
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Her emotions keep her pretty busy.</font>

443
00:30:51,305 --> 00:30:53,705
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I think that's what's so great about her.</font>

444
00:30:54,939 --> 00:30:56,105
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Yeah.</font>

445
00:31:01,238 --> 00:31:02,438
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I'm sorry.</font>

446
00:31:03,939 --> 00:31:05,905
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Maybe I didn't have to worry.</font>

447
00:31:07,872 --> 00:31:10,939
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">It feels to me now like she
and I are family.</font>

448
00:31:12,605 --> 00:31:16,271
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">When she first came to our shop,
she was totally hopeless.</font>

449
00:31:16,939 --> 00:31:20,538
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Every day she broke dishes
and confused orders.</font>

450
00:31:22,438 --> 00:31:27,138
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">But she told me that she couldn't
let her parents find out,</font>

451
00:31:27,472 --> 00:31:29,605
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">and she worked her butt off every day.</font>

452
00:31:36,238 --> 00:31:39,039
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">You know,
Nao has a kind of mysterious power.</font>

453
00:31:46,039 --> 00:31:46,939
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I lied.</font>

454
00:31:49,472 --> 00:31:51,505
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">-I lied to you.
-Huh?</font>

455
00:31:53,839 --> 00:31:55,805
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I'm <i>not OK with this!</i></font>

456
00:31:56,105 --> 00:31:57,405
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Jeez, dude.</font>

457
00:32:01,205 --> 00:32:04,271
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Oh, Marina
and Mitsuishi said they're going home.</font>

458
00:32:04,338 --> 00:32:05,638
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">They were really lovey-dovey.</font>

459
00:32:05,705 --> 00:32:09,039
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">-Why don't we go home too?
-OK.</font>

460
00:32:11,105 --> 00:32:13,005
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I'll leave you guys here.</font>

461
00:32:15,438 --> 00:32:18,672
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I'll say bye to you now.</font>

462
00:32:22,638 --> 00:32:27,005
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I like Evening Star ramen, but...</font>

463
00:32:28,538 --> 00:32:33,405
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I won't go there again
until I can get over you, Issei.</font>

464
00:32:34,805 --> 00:32:35,872
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Yukari--</font>

465
00:32:35,939 --> 00:32:37,805
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Thank you for everything today.</font>

466
00:32:39,738 --> 00:32:42,905
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Thank you for all the good food
you've made for me.</font>

467
00:32:48,805 --> 00:32:50,638
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Wait, Yukari!</font>

468
00:32:53,572 --> 00:32:55,672
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I can't let it end like this.</font>

469
00:32:57,472 --> 00:32:58,472
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Nao.</font>

470
00:33:00,638 --> 00:33:07,538
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Yukari has been very frank about
how much she likes you, Issei.</font>

471
00:33:10,039 --> 00:33:11,672
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">So you need to be frank with her too.</font>

472
00:33:17,138 --> 00:33:18,472
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">What are you talking about?</font>

473
00:33:19,305 --> 00:33:22,538
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I'm very sorry, Yukari.</font>

474
00:33:23,105 --> 00:33:24,305
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I...</font>

475
00:33:25,171 --> 00:33:26,772
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I'm sorry!</font>

476
00:33:32,205 --> 00:33:34,872
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I lied to you.</font>

477
00:33:36,905 --> 00:33:38,171
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">To tell you the truth...</font>

478
00:33:39,638 --> 00:33:41,638
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">she's not my girlfriend at all.</font>

479
00:33:43,872 --> 00:33:46,138
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I didn't want to hurt you, Yukari.</font>

480
00:33:47,039 --> 00:33:48,305
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">So I made this all up.</font>

481
00:33:51,271 --> 00:33:53,772
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">But I know that was way more cruel.</font>

482
00:33:56,338 --> 00:34:00,472
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I'm terribly sorry, Yukari.</font>

483
00:34:09,939 --> 00:34:11,138
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">You see, Yukari--</font>

484
00:34:11,205 --> 00:34:12,839
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">That's enough.</font>

485
00:34:12,905 --> 00:34:15,472
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">-Huh?
-They need to settle this on their own.</font>

486
00:34:16,605 --> 00:34:18,505
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">-But--
-This has nothing to do with us now.</font>

487
00:34:19,738 --> 00:34:20,939
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">"Us"?</font>

488
00:34:23,738 --> 00:34:25,872
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Hey! Wait!</font>

489
00:34:26,238 --> 00:34:27,905
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Sorry, Issei and Yukari!</font>

490
00:34:27,972 --> 00:34:29,839
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Wait! Wait! Yukari!</font>

491
00:34:30,438 --> 00:34:33,672
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I'm really glad
I was able to talk with you.</font>

492
00:34:35,171 --> 00:34:36,572
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I mean it. Really!</font>

493
00:34:50,638 --> 00:34:52,805
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I understand what you're telling me...</font>

494
00:34:53,605 --> 00:34:57,205
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">but it still doesn't make sense.</font>

495
00:34:58,939 --> 00:35:00,839
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Everything is my fault.</font>

496
00:35:01,472 --> 00:35:03,305
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I forced her to do this.</font>

497
00:35:03,371 --> 00:35:04,839
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">That's not what I mean.</font>

498
00:35:05,972 --> 00:35:07,438
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Were you actually acting?</font>

499
00:35:08,405 --> 00:35:09,271
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Huh?</font>

500
00:35:09,438 --> 00:35:14,171
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Are you sure you really have no feelings
for Nao?</font>

501
00:35:15,438 --> 00:35:18,972
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Well, I mean, she's got Uehara.</font>

502
00:35:19,105 --> 00:35:22,205
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">And besides, to me,
she's just a co-worker.</font>

503
00:35:25,839 --> 00:35:28,171
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Let's face it, ramen is my only love.</font>

504
00:35:28,238 --> 00:35:31,572
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Or to put it another way,
ramen is my girlfriend.</font>

505
00:35:37,705 --> 00:35:41,505
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">So, you won't even acknowledge it
yourself, huh?</font>

506
00:35:42,138 --> 00:35:43,338
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Huh?</font>

507
00:35:46,171 --> 00:35:47,705
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Nothing.</font>

508
00:35:50,305 --> 00:35:54,705
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I thought you were
more of a man than that, Issei.</font>

509
00:35:55,072 --> 00:35:55,905
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">What?</font>

510
00:35:56,039 --> 00:35:57,305
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Good bye.</font>

511
00:35:58,638 --> 00:36:00,072
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Huh? Hold on!</font>

512
00:36:02,705 --> 00:36:04,072
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">What's that all about?</font>

513
00:36:06,505 --> 00:36:08,405
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">-Issei.
-Huh?</font>

514
00:36:08,472 --> 00:36:12,805
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">-Oh, it's just you.
-Did you just get dumped by your stalker?</font>

515
00:36:13,205 --> 00:36:14,505
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">No!</font>

516
00:36:14,572 --> 00:36:16,738
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Where the hell were you, anyway?</font>

517
00:36:16,805 --> 00:36:20,538
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">-Let me tell you what happened to me.
-Huh?</font>

518
00:36:20,605 --> 00:36:24,672
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I was just... dumped by a ghost.</font>

519
00:36:25,505 --> 00:36:28,105
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">-What?
-Oh, I have an idea!</font>

520
00:36:28,271 --> 00:36:32,338
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">How about you and me swap sob stories?</font>

521
00:36:32,405 --> 00:36:34,171
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Hey! I did not just get dumped!</font>

522
00:36:34,238 --> 00:36:36,205
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">-Yes you did.
-Shut up, you jerk.</font>

523
00:36:42,972 --> 00:36:46,271
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">What are you grinning about.
It's creeping me out.</font>

524
00:36:47,238 --> 00:36:49,171
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Well, you came and found me.</font>

525
00:36:49,338 --> 00:36:50,238
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Found you?</font>

526
00:36:51,472 --> 00:36:53,238
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">When I first met you,</font>

527
00:36:53,305 --> 00:36:55,538
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I could never tell
what you were thinking.</font>

528
00:36:55,605 --> 00:36:57,705
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">You would never
pay attention to me either.</font>

529
00:36:57,772 --> 00:37:00,672
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">But to me at the time, that was enough.</font>

530
00:37:01,772 --> 00:37:06,039
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">In fact, it's like a miracle to me
that we've ended up like this.</font>

531
00:37:07,039 --> 00:37:10,305
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">So I've decided to enjoy myself now,
no matter what happens.</font>

532
00:37:10,371 --> 00:37:12,271
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">You sure are on top of the world.</font>

533
00:37:12,338 --> 00:37:14,705
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Also, I was really happy today.</font>

534
00:37:14,839 --> 00:37:15,972
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">About what?</font>

535
00:37:16,672 --> 00:37:20,438
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Because you found me in the dark
at the haunted house.</font>

536
00:37:21,005 --> 00:37:24,138
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">It was like you could sense me,
and feel my presence.</font>

537
00:37:24,205 --> 00:37:26,205
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">That's how you found me, right?</font>

538
00:37:27,271 --> 00:37:28,472
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Oh, you!</font>

539
00:37:34,839 --> 00:37:36,805
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Hey... Wait!</font>

540
00:37:45,605 --> 00:37:47,705
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">It sure is taking long.</font>

541
00:37:50,972 --> 00:37:52,238
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Nao.</font>

542
00:37:52,305 --> 00:37:53,505
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Huh?</font>

543
00:37:53,939 --> 00:37:55,405
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I want you to quit.</font>

544
00:37:55,905 --> 00:37:57,005
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">What?</font>

545
00:37:58,305 --> 00:37:59,538
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Quit that job.</font>

546
00:38:00,805 --> 00:38:01,939
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Why?</font>

547
00:38:02,005 --> 00:38:05,005
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">You can get a job somewhere else.</font>

548
00:38:05,672 --> 00:38:07,305
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Like a cafe with just women.</font>

549
00:38:21,605 --> 00:38:22,438
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">What's with you?</font>

550
00:38:24,638 --> 00:38:25,805
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I was...</font>

551
00:38:26,672 --> 00:38:30,538
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I was just thinking
how boyfriend-like that was.</font>

552
00:38:30,605 --> 00:38:31,438
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">You're goofy.</font>

553
00:38:34,472 --> 00:38:36,472
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Hold the elevator!</font>

554
00:38:36,839 --> 00:38:38,939
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Sorry. Let me squeeze in here.</font>

555
00:38:42,872 --> 00:38:43,872
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Sorry.</font>

556
00:39:03,672 --> 00:39:05,438
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Young people these days.</font>

557
00:39:08,772 --> 00:39:10,572
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">CLOSE</font>

558
00:39:15,805 --> 00:39:17,672
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">THREE WEEKS LATER
THE NEW SCHOOL YEAR</font>

559
00:39:18,005 --> 00:39:20,538
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I'm so happy that I can hardly stand it!</font>

560
00:39:24,638 --> 00:39:27,039
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I never thought I'd be with you
and Mitsuishi our senior year too.</font>

561
00:39:27,105 --> 00:39:28,271
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I'm so happy!</font>

562
00:39:28,338 --> 00:39:30,505
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I'm super happy too!</font>

563
00:39:30,572 --> 00:39:34,772
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">We can complain about our boyfriends
every day now.</font>

564
00:39:34,839 --> 00:39:36,638
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Then wouldn't it be better
if I wasn't here?</font>

565
00:39:36,705 --> 00:39:39,672
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Hey! I'm with you guys this year too!</font>

566
00:39:39,738 --> 00:39:42,738
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Oh, but Uehara is still
in a different class.</font>

567
00:39:42,805 --> 00:39:45,438
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Yeah, but I'm perfectly fine with that.</font>

568
00:39:45,505 --> 00:39:48,538
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">He promised to be with me at lunch
and when we go home.</font>

569
00:39:48,605 --> 00:39:50,839
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">You're acting like you've got it made.</font>

570
00:39:50,905 --> 00:39:53,605
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Did you two get closer over spring break?</font>

571
00:39:53,672 --> 00:39:55,205
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Yeah, I guess.</font>

572
00:39:56,572 --> 00:39:58,605
<font face="sans-serif" size="71"><i>Is Yoshikawa Nao in here?</i></font>

573
00:40:04,305 --> 00:40:07,638
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">-Do you know her, Nao?
-No.</font>

574
00:40:09,039 --> 00:40:10,972
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I've never seen her before,
but she's a real cutie.</font>

575
00:40:11,672 --> 00:40:13,105
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">She sure looks pissed off though.</font>

576
00:40:13,972 --> 00:40:14,872
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Huh?</font>

577
00:40:14,939 --> 00:40:16,872
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Do you know who Yoshikawa Nao is?</font>

578
00:40:17,939 --> 00:40:19,472
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">That's her over there.</font>

579
00:40:22,338 --> 00:40:23,572
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">What's going on?</font>

580
00:40:27,138 --> 00:40:28,839
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">-Oh, she's coming!
-She's coming over here!</font>

581
00:40:30,572 --> 00:40:32,572
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Oh, dear! Oh, dear!</font>

582
00:40:35,505 --> 00:40:37,371
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Are you Yoshikawa Nao?</font>

583
00:40:40,171 --> 00:40:41,271
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Yes.</font>

584
00:40:41,472 --> 00:40:42,572
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Come with me for a minute.</font>

585
00:40:46,171 --> 00:40:48,538
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">"Come with me"?</font>

586
00:40:55,872 --> 00:40:59,072
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I'm Kitaura Nozomi.</font>

587
00:41:00,171 --> 00:41:02,205
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Kitaura?</font>

588
00:41:02,271 --> 00:41:04,605
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I transferred in here this spring.</font>

589
00:41:04,672 --> 00:41:08,738
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Oh... you're a transfer student.</font>

590
00:41:08,972 --> 00:41:11,171
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">No wonder I've never seen you.</font>

591
00:41:14,338 --> 00:41:17,305
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">So,
what did you want to talk to me about?</font>

592
00:41:22,371 --> 00:41:23,772
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Is it true...</font>

593
00:41:25,205 --> 00:41:27,205
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">that you're dating Uehara Hisashi?</font>

594
00:41:28,505 --> 00:41:29,672
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Huh?</font>

595
00:41:33,872 --> 00:41:37,171
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Uh... well...</font>

596
00:43:05,371 --> 00:43:07,872
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">THIS IS A FICTIONAL DRAMA.</font>
